text: Jesús Vázquez (born 30 October 1969) is a Mexican former cyclist. He competed in the team pursuit at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Mexico Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Mexican track cyclists
